data.hoverText: 可与单数或复数动词连用的可数名词

data.chText: （尤指苏格兰的）宗族，氏族，家族
data.enText: a group of families who are related to each other, especially in Scotland

data.chText: 庞大的家族；宗派；帮派；小集团
data.enText: a very large family, or a group of people who are connected because of a particular thing

data.chText: 脱离了好莱坞的那帮人数日益增多的明星中的一员
data.enText: one of a growing clan of stars who have left Hollywood

means: (尤指苏格兰的)宗族，氏族，家族

tr: group of people related by blood or marriage

value.def: A clan is a group which consists of families that are related to each other.
You can refer to a group of people with the same interests as a clan .

example.ex: ...a powerful clan of industrialists from Monterrey.
example.tran: 来自蒙特雷的势力强大的企业家集团

value.tran: (有共同利益的)集团，帮派，派系
